snippet.title: Pull My Tongue - Trailer
snippet.description:
iTunes: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/pull-my-tongue/id1046617847?ls=1&mt=8
A Game by David Marquardt and Noodlecake Studios.

Help feed Greg by pulling his tongue through a series of fun puzzles that include, zappers, spikes, chewing gum, balloons and more!

Key Features:

- 5 worlds with 90 levels
- Cute and cuddly character
- Deliciously unique tongue physics (yes there is such a thing)
- Never before seen gameplay and puzzles
